urch of Satan(1966) 同The Satanic Temple(2013)<br />\n<br />\n兩個派別都唔相信有神同afterlife，撒旦只係一個symbol唔係d咩邪惡魔鬼，但CoS就有d黑魔法儀式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，TST就無<br />\n<br />\nTST更加係美國認可既宗教機構，有得免稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />短短六年就超越CoS變咗最大既Satanism教會<br />\n<br />\nTST教條其實係一d好簡單既做人道理，好岩公民社會，都係基於自由平等同互相尊重，凡事獨立思考科學求真，幾實幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thesatanictemple.com/pages/tenets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthesatanictemple.com%2Fpages%2Ftenets&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=8b054810\" target=\"_blank\">https://thesatanictemple.com/pages/tenets</a><br />\n<br />\nTHERE ARE SEVEN FUNDAMENTAL TENETS<br />\n<br />\nI<br />\nOne should strive to act with compassion and empathy toward all creatures in accordance with reason.<br />\nII<br />\nThe struggle for justice is an ongoing and necessary pursuit that should prevail over laws and institutions.<br />\nIII<br />\nOne&rsquo;s body is inviolable, subject to one&rsquo;s own will alone.<br />\nIV<br />\nThe freedoms of others should be respected, including the freedom to offend. To willfully and unjustly encroach upon the freedoms of another is to forgo one's own.<br />\nV<br />\nBeliefs should conform to one's best scientific understanding of the world. One should take care never to distort scientific facts to fit one's beliefs.<br />\nVI<br />\nPeople are fallible. If one makes a mistake, one should do one's best to rectify it and resolve any harm that might have been caused.<br />\nVII<br />\nEvery tenet is a guiding principle designed to inspire nobility in action and thought. The spirit of compassion, wisdom, and justice should always prevail over the written or spoken word.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/thesatanictemple\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fthesatanictemple&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=03c5d5bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/thesatanictemple</a><br />\nTST仲有instagram，d人都係goth/metalhead咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽開metal既我表示好正，好想入會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我就唔係好明，佢地教義都唔係d咩獨有既野，如果係咁，呢班人入呢個「教」，係為左乜呢，係咪一種有同伴既心靈慰藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定其實似一個學會多d?好似共濟會個d咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過TST就politically active過共濟會，會爭取宗教多元平等個d<br />\n<br />\n好有趣，再研究下有無類似既宗教先！"},{"pid":"4f8e1fa4fbc099bd7fb1ab884a8c1908e5dc56c7","tid":2003413,"uid":22302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c835a372d42928e81e0d7d831ff330f476cdcbbc","tid":2003413,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2237fe274ddeb9a33162eaa3583c2e06ca7dd1f0","tid":2003413,"uid":167904,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"dc491379b257a405bdac6d55b729a0627c158caa","tid":2003413,"uid":22302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T01:07:38.000Z","msg":"佢問宗教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"科學都係一種信仰"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"咁咩都係宗教啦ching"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"有時真係忍唔住笑"},{"pid":"21ae9f1ce7c166d012dabea4a4ca388663534d1b","tid":2003413,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:01:33.000Z","msg":"而家開始相信神, 但係唔係神"},{"pid":"9ff86508c5a06558d36a717194ad2d4b5e4f0566","tid":2003413,"uid":202904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:07:41.000Z","msg":"飛天意大利麵神教"},{"pid":"f674952b13ed3bc73fb4d9c21fc4c5fb17763dd0","tid":2003413,"uid":100766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"一個標明冇afterlife嘅宗教冇人會去信<br />\n因為對死後嘅未知嘅恐懼<br />\n人類先會創造神呢個角色同伸延出黎嘅afterlife<br />\n<br />\n如果人死真係如燈滅，咁仲信宗教黎做乜<br />\n基本上你仲可以作奸犯科冇後果添"}]}